9849","tid":323374,"uid":8815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:23:10.000Z","msg":"23男<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/232257_1c61e5b0e939fd51ba166796ff45c36b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F232257_1c61e5b0e939fd51ba166796ff45c36b.jpg&h=5262d3ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/232257_a95145ccb19e436546964c81f0859ea0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F232257_a95145ccb19e436546964c81f0859ea0.jpg&h=80590a15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b6f6efee3b5a9712aac25c1b09498136cb4f5f4","tid":323374,"uid":127601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:39:32.000Z","msg":"毒L突然有街出，明天先睇果十隻掌。 頭十位名額已滿，有緣下次再睇其他。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61df8474be1bde44b6f842bb8fd8962bcab948d6","tid":323374,"uid":127601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T14:40:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/222449_99eaa75f0e50c55dfad1fd5fa2ef87d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F222449_99eaa75f0e50c55dfad1fd5fa2ef87d1.jpg&h=06fa0af4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/222450_2d16e1a47d54250fcc9fe91e84996317.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F222450_2d16e1a47d54250fcc9fe91e84996317.jpg&h=b1526fa8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n1. 個人比較宅男,唔識同人相處,而且口才唔得。<br />\n2. 所以好多時,見到喜歡的女仔,唔敢表達,因為自卑心強<br />\n3. 所以造成將對方放左係個心度好耐,經常性掛住<br />\n4. 份人思想好多,經常性FF,大多雜念。<br />\n5. 30歲前事業心唔強, 工作對你來講可有可無。<br />\n6. 須然口才唔好,但其實份人轉數幾快,有小聰明<br />\n7. 預測到時拍拖,唔係因為有感情,而係因為性而走埋一齊.所以要自我控制,本身份人的自制力又唔強"},{"pid":"1be25243c1fb92e30c44e1b0618ef1848459f81f","tid":323374,"uid":127601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T14:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/f5t8l7wk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ff5t8l7wk&h=cb8690b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://holland.pk/wy01n8hl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwy01n8hl&h=a5e7beaa&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n1. 現在個運不錯,幾享受現在生活<br />\n2. 個人享受自由,非常獨立,而好有自信<br />\n3. 細個因為性格偏激,造成俾人誤會,留係個心度憤憤不平<br />\n4. 小個身體唔好,好多病痛<br />\n5. 做事成日都臨尾香,所以好容易做到最後先來無信心或轉態"},{"pid":"3e8d9c30576d576a179d0a9acaca08e0a9b1c980","tid":323374,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T14:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/225748_9fc599e764eedd8bb5bbd0972f007c52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F225748_9fc599e764eedd8bb5bbd0972f007c52.jpg&h=fd0cf084&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/225749_9fc599e764eedd8bb5bbd0972f007c52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F225749_9fc599e764eedd8bb5bbd0972f007c52.jpg&h=151b6025&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c16edf5870f7b1ba49a14a19bcef1d84252ef86","tid":323374,"uid":127395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T14:58:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/222449_99eaa75f0e50c55dfad1fd5fa2ef87d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F222449_99eaa75f0e50c55dfad1fd5fa2ef87d1.jpg&h=06fa0af4&s={SIZE}\" />[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/222450_2d16e1a47d54250fcc9fe91e84996317.jpg[/ig]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F222450_2d16e1a47d54250fcc9fe91e84996317.jpg%5B%2Fig%5D&d=qjxrd%2BhD2PRDCrhTAv49lgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=20ff147a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/222450_2d16e1a47d54250fcc9fe91e84996317.jpg[/ig]</a></blockquote><br />\n1. 個人比較宅男,唔識同人相處,而且口才唔得。<br />\n2. 所以好多時,見到喜歡的女仔,唔敢表達,因為自卑心強<br />\n3. 所以造成將對方放左係個心度好耐,經常性掛住<br />\n4. 份人思想好多,經常性FF,大多雜念。<br />\n5. 30歲前事業心唔強, 工作對你來講可有可無。<br />\n6. 須然口才唔好,但其實份人轉數幾快,有小聰明<br />\n7. 預測到時拍拖,唔係因為有感情,而係因為性而走埋一齊.所以要自我控制,本身份人的自制力又唔強</blockquote><br />\n1234都中<br />\n5 我好想搵到工 不過好難搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n7都中中地嘅其實 之前有試過類似咁<br />\nThx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就咁睇我好似無樣好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369cf9ff18eab4aab5ced92aca9c9798d41f70eb","tid":323374,"uid":127601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T15:02:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1. 30歲前經常FF,不過30歲後現實返好多<br />\n2. 如果有拍拖,現在個感情唔順利,身體都唔係太好<br />\n3. 細個身體都唔好,而且發育得好早<br />\n4. 個心臟都唔好,有畏高或唔可以玩D 刺激既野<br />\n5. 做事唔夠膽,信心都唔夠<br />\n6. 非常之相信命運,而且術數緣都強"},{"pid":"b83695bc8fb822c477249ec87a2dd70c0bfd7231","tid":323374,"uid":127601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T15:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/gvqtlmzd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgvqtlmzd&h=46c69e41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tp5f2mk3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftp5f2mk3&h=b99c3352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n21男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1. 個人原則性好強,目標好清晰<br />\n2. 對以前發生的事記得好深刻<br />\n3. 30歲後開始會發現自己好喜歡或好多機會去旅行<br />\n4. 好喜歡神祕玄學野<br />\n5. 好痴情,但又無膽去鍾意人<br />\n6. 好早已經多思多慮,好多煩惱好多煩倩感<br />\n7. 父母關係好早已經出問題,有點兒孤兒仔性格"},{"pid":"e923d396f48c2e95562a4c43adf75d4792e91774","tid":323374,"uid":127601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T15:22:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/9zlpej0n\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9zlpej0n&h=5a94f6d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/klhuaebx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fklhuaebx&h=77423eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n感謝</blockquote><br />\n1. 好敏感,甚至有D 神經質<br />\n2. 好愛自由,細細個已經好獨立,好自主<br />\n3. 唔鍾意行路,但除左行街SHOPPING<br />\n4. 好難儲到錢,因為一有錢就會駛晒佢<br />\n5. 好容易就會轉態或俾人說服,成日決定好既人,第二日就會改,定力唔夠<br />\n6. 要多做運動,唔係好易身體出問題,而且訓練自己意志力"},{"pid":"bf87372ea2178cf6d97fd4969f63c4df35c2ba69","tid":323374,"uid":5806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T15:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/232452_24d680faf364829cd5d5aefd6a94084f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F232452_24d680faf364829cd5d5aefd6a94084f.jpg&h=690bafbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc835dc60d1e8e747d2906cbcd4fe3c268826a33","tid":323374,"uid":127601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T15:30:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/223638_271af314ea040f554be57ddf4a958a65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2