s/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5. 聰明,轉數快,而且口才都唔差<br />\n6. 物質慾強,對自己唔差,留意注意腸胃問題"},{"pid":"46cc0b5cc4a74452d2fa97c633904ce3cb8f5cc2","tid":323374,"uid":127395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T15:57:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/222449_99eaa75f0e50c55dfad1fd5fa2ef87d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F222449_99eaa75f0e50c55dfad1fd5fa2ef87d1.jpg&h=06fa0af4&s={SIZE}\" />[img][url]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/222450_2d16e1a47d54250fcc9fe91e84996317.jpg[/ig][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F222450_2d16e1a47d54250fcc9fe91e84996317.jpg%5B%2Fig%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=qjxrd%2BhD2PRDCrhTAv49lgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=49ba32fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/222450_2d16e1a47d54250fcc9fe91e84996317.jpg[/ig][/url]</a></blockquote><br />\n1. 個人比較宅男,唔識同人相處,而且口才唔得。<br />\n2. 所以好多時,見到喜歡的女仔,唔敢表達,因為自卑心強<br />\n3. 所以造成將對方放左係個心度好耐,經常性掛住<br />\n4. 份人思想好多,經常性FF,大多雜念。<br />\n5. 30歲前事業心唔強, 工作對你來講可有可無。<br />\n6. 須然口才唔好,但其實份人轉數幾快,有小聰明<br />\n7. 預測到時拍拖,唔係因為有感情,而係因為性而走埋一齊.所以要自我控制,本身份人的自制力又唔強</blockquote><br />\n1234都中<br />\n5 我好想搵到工 不過好難搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n7都中中地嘅其實 之前有試過類似咁<br />\nThx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就咁睇我好似無樣好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBtw我係咪事業感情財運都好差"},{"pid":"040e9df3ed7bf2f4c034ef6824b0dc35c45d50dc","tid":323374,"uid":127601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:01:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/222449_99eaa75f0e50c55dfad1fd5fa2ef87d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F222449_99eaa75f0e50c55dfad1fd5fa2ef87d1.jpg&h=06fa0af4&s={SIZE}\" />[img][url]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/222450_2d16e1a47d54250fcc9fe91e84996317.jpg[/ig][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F222450_2d16e1a47d54250fcc9fe91e84996317.jpg%5B%2Fig%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=qjxrd%2BhD2PRDCrhTAv49lgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=49ba32fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/222450_2d16e1a47d54250fcc9fe91e84996317.jpg[/ig][/url]</a></blockquote><br />\n1. 個人比較宅男,唔識同人相處,而且口才唔得。<br />\n2. 所以好多時,見到喜歡的女仔,唔敢表達,因為自卑心強<br />\n3. 所以造成將對方放左係個心度好耐,經常性掛住<br />\n4. 份人思想好多,經常性FF,大多雜念。<br />\n5. 30歲前事業心唔強, 工作對你來講可有可無。<br />\n6. 須然口才唔好,但其實份人轉數幾快,有小聰明<br />\n7. 預測到時拍拖,唔係因為有感情,而係因為性而走埋一齊.所以要自我控制,本身份人的自制力又唔強</blockquote><br />\n1234都中<br />\n5 我好想搵到工 不過好難搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n7都中中地嘅其實 之前有試過類似咁<br />\nThx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就咁睇我好似無樣好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBtw我係咪事業感情財運都好差</blockquote><br />\n手掌係睇個心,你自己的心太雜亂,所以D 掌紋就亂咁來。收心養性,唔係行運個運都行唔長。30歲前你工作運唔太好,做二做就想轉第二份。其實末必關份工事,係你自己心末定。"},{"pid":"c3effb0df5633e725d46ee926401b4194765c438","tid":323374,"uid":127395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score